WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
I love you so much

00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:16.000
which really means

00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:28.600
I am partly mistaking you for

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
somebody else

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:45.660
I will later blame you for not being who I imagined

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.500
without checking you were.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.540
I will try to change you

00:01:00.700 --> 00:01:05.000
i will

00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:07.100
try

00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:10.900
to posses you

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:12.900
then resent you

00:01:12.900 --> 00:01:14.800
for trapping me

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.100
i will

00:01:17.100 --> 00:01:19.800
one day

00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:21.900
think of other people

00:01:21.900 --> 00:01:25.260
when  we make love

00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:29.120
I will expect you to understand

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:31.900
what I am feeling

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.000
without me

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:38.400
ever telling you

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:45.000
I will attribute all my joys

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:46.400
and more particularly

00:01:46.400 --> 00:01:50.200
all my sorrows to you

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:56.300
it will always be your fault

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:01.000
I will use you to pretend we are not all

00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:03.500
fundamentally alone.

00:02:08.700 --> 00:02:12.100
I will blame you for having ruined my life

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:13.800
and you will do the same

00:02:15.700 --> 00:02:22.800
please be my valentine

